Rules.InvariantScript:
Set(StatusChoice, DropdownStatus.SelectedText.'data-ADB4D7A662F548B49FAC2B986E348A1BResult');

ClearCollect(
    colTickets,
    ForAll(
        Table(
            ParseJSON(
                SearchFilterTicketsSPList.Run(
                    If(
                        IsBlank(SearchQuery),
                        "___",
                        SearchQuery
                    ), StatusChoice, TagChoice
                ).searchresults
            )
        ),
        {
            ID: Value(Value.ID),
            Title: Text(Value.title),
            Description: Text(Value.description),
            MainCategory: Value(Value.mainCategory),
            DateCreated: DateValue(Value.dateCreated),
            CreatorId: Value(Value.creatorId),
            Status: Text(Value.status),
            AssignedTo: Value(Value.assignedTo),
            LastUpdated: DateValue(Value.lastUpdated),
            LocationId: Value(Value.locationId),
            Tags: Text(Value.tags),
            AddAssignees: Text(Value.addAssignees)
        }
    )
)

Set(TagChoice, DropdownTag.SelectedText.Value);

ClearCollect(
    colTickets,
    ForAll(
        Table(
            ParseJSON(
                SearchFilterTicketsSPList.Run(
                    If(
                        IsBlank(SearchQuery),
                        "___",
                        SearchQuery
                    ), StatusChoice, TagChoice
                ).searchresults
            )
        ),
        {
            ID: Value(Value.ID),
            Title: Text(Value.title),
            Description: Text(Value.description),
            MainCategory: Value(Value.mainCategory),
            DateCreated: DateValue(Value.dateCreated),
            CreatorId: Value(Value.creatorId),
            Status: Text(Value.status),
            AssignedTo: Value(Value.assignedTo),
            LastUpdated: DateValue(Value.lastUpdated),
            LocationId: Value(Value.locationId),
            Tags: Text(Value.tags),
            AddAssignees: Text(Value.addAssignees)
        }
    )
)
If(App.ActiveScreen.Name = "MyTickets" && compFilterMenu.CheckAdmin, Parent.Height - FilterHeader.Height - TicketsSelection.Height, Parent.Height - FilterHeader.Height)

If(
    App.ActiveScreen.Name = "MyTickets" && (!compFilterMenu.CheckAdmin && (!(DropdownStatus.SelectedText.'data-ADB4D7A662F548B49FAC2B986E348A1BResult' = "open") || !(RadioTickets.SelectedText.Value = "My Tickets") || !(DropdownTag.SelectedText.Value = "None")) || compFilterMenu.CheckAdmin && (!(DropdownStatus.SelectedText.'data-ADB4D7A662F548B49FAC2B986E348A1BResult' = "open") || !(RadioTickets.SelectedText.Value = "My Assigned") || !(DropdownTag.SelectedText.Value = "None"))) || !(App.ActiveScreen.Name = "MyTickets") && (!(DropdownStatus.SelectedText.'data-ADB4D7A662F548B49FAC2B986E348A1BResult' = "open") || !(RadioTickets.SelectedText.Value = "Tickets") || !(DropdownTag.SelectedText.Value = "None")),
    Icon.FilterFlatFilled,
    Icon.FilterFlat
)

If(
    compFilterMenu.CheckAdmin && App.ActiveScreen.Name = "MyTickets",
    If(
        App.Height > 560,
        400,
        320
    ),
    !compFilterMenu.CheckAdmin && App.ActiveScreen.Name = "MyTickets",
    150,
    If(
        App.Height > 560,
        420,
        320
    )
)

CustomProperties.Name: FilterVisible
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Determines if menu should be visible or not

CustomProperties.Name: CheckAdmin
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Checks if user is either admin/tech

CustomProperties.Name: NewHeight
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Set the height of the component

CustomProperties.Name: TicketsChoice
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Returns the chosen selection of tickets

CustomProperties.Name: FilterIconSize
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Sets the size of the filter icon
